## POST 登录

POST /auth/login

HB

> Body 请求参数

```yaml
username: test
password: testpassword
captchaValue: "{{captchaValue}}"
captchKey: "{{captchaKey}}"

```

|名称|位置|类型|必选|说明|
|---|---|---|---|---|
|token|header|string| 否 |none|
|authorization|header|string| 否 |none|
|body|body|object| 否 |none|
|» username|body|string| 否 |none|
|» password|body|string| 否 |none|
|» captchaValue|body|string| 是 |none|
|» captchKey|body|string| 是 |none|

## POST 空域转换-创建/更新

POST /api/biz/airspace/syncAirspaceConvert

这个接口支持创建 / 更新

> Body 请求参数

```json
{
  "airspaceId": "01K9685T8TR2PFEVR6QK0B30BN",
  "originalType": "R",
  "newType": "F",
  "startTime": "2025-10-20 09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-11-05 18:00:00",
  "forbiddenStartTime": "06:00:00",
  "forbiddenEndTime": "20:00:00",
  "reason": "重要活动需要临时管制",
  "forbiddenModels": "大型无人机,中型无人机",
  "flightMode": "目视飞行",
  "speedLimit": "80km/h",
  "fuelLimit": "20L",
  "uavSpeedLimit": 100,
  "thSpeedLimit": 700,
  "visibilityRequirement": "5km",
  "specialDescription": "活动期间禁止一切低空飞行活动",
  "userType": "ATC"
}
```

|» approvaUnit|body|string| 否 | 批件下发单位|武基  军参 其它......|

#### 详细说明

**» airspaceType**: 空域类型：F管制区,P适飞区,E专属区,C管控区,L起降场,R航线,O障碍物,T临时禁飞区  

airspaceType = '空域' → 查 F/P/E/C/L/O/T

airspaceType = '航线' → 查 R
airspaceType = '管制区' → 查 R
airspaceType = '非管制区' → 查 R
airspaceType = '全部' → 不加条件
